<h3>Roofing</h3>
<p>Long sales cycles benefit from AI nurture sequences. Specialized features: damage estimate workflows, insurance claim coordination, post-storm marketing automation.</p>
<h3>Pest Control</h3>
<p>Recurring service model benefits from AI customer retention. Specialized features: treatment recurrence scheduling, seasonal pest predictions.</p>
<h3>Cleaning Services</h3>
<p>High customer churn rate makes AI retention critical. Specialized features: cleaning preference profiles, recurring service optimization.</p>
<h3>Lawn Care</h3>
<p>Weather and seasonality drive operations. AI predicts service timing and customer communication.</p>
<p>The right stack depends on trade. Generic home service AI advice misses trade-specific opportunities.</p>
